description:
On today’s show, Dr. Emily is talking about the love languages –because there are so many ways to give and receive.

She talks about how figuring out each other’s love languages can immensely help make your relationship stronger, why it’s important for both people to make an effort in fixing a relationship, and how learning to love going down on each other can be one of the best steps you take in your sex life. 


Follow Emily on all social @sexwithemily

For even more sex advice, tips & tricks, visit sexwithemily.com
